      </style></div><div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center lg:mt-28 mb-12"><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start"><img src="/car-images/volkswagen-hero.jpg" alt="Volkswagen used auto parts hero image" class="w-full max-w-md rounded-2xl shadow-xl"/></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-center"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl md:text-2xl mb-3 text-white">Volkswagen Used Parts for Sale</h3><p class="text-[18px] leading-[30px] text-[#cecece]">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral. Volkswagen owners appreciate the perfect balance of German engineering, design, and driving fun. At PartsCentral, we help you maintain that experience with high-quality OEM Volkswagen used parts inspected, approved, and shipped across the U.S. From the iconic Beetle to modern SUVs, your VW is in good hands.</p></div></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-14"><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Smart. Affordable. Reliable. That’s PartsCentral.</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>OEM Volkswagen used parts inspected and approved</li><li>Nationwide shipping across the United States</li><li>German-engineered performance without dealer pricing</li><li>Designed to preserve Volkswagen handling and reliability</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Precision-Engineered. Budget-Friendly.</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Volkswagen drivers demand more than basic performance; they want durability, refined handling, and a unique driving feel. Our VW used parts are OEM-matched, thoroughly tested, and ready to keep your ride as sharp as day one without draining your wallet.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Volkswagen Parts We Carry</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Engines, transmissions, cooling systems</li><li>Radiators, fans, AC compressors</li><li>Window regulators and motors</li><li>Starters, alternators, sensors, switches</li><li>Doors, bumpers, fenders, mirrors</li><li>Suspension, control arms, axles</li><li>Headlights, taillights, interior trim</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Thoroughly Inspected by Experts</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Every used VW part is hand-inspected by our in-house team to ensure proper fit, performance, and safety so you can drive with full confidence. Only quality parts make it to your doorstep.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Get Dealer-Level Performance Without Dealer Pricing</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Why pay full price for new when Volkswagen used auto parts work just as well? Get a quick quote in minutes — no account needed. Shipped fast, backed by support, priced right.</p></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Volkswagen Models We Support</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">We stock Volkswagen used parts for most VW models. Have a vintage or rare model? Let us help you locate it.</p><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-1 text-[#cecece]"><li>Volkswagen Atlas</li><li>Volkswagen Beetle</li><li>Volkswagen CC</li><li>Volkswagen EOS</li><li>Volkswagen Golf</li><li>Volkswagen GTI</li><li>Volkswagen Jetta</li><li>Volkswagen Passat</li><li>Volkswagen Phaeton</li><li>Volkswagen Routan</li><li>Volkswagen Tiguan</li><li>Volkswagen Touareg</li><li>Volkswagen Rabbit</li><li>Volkswagen Scirocco</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Why VW Owners Trust PartsCentral</h3><ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-[#cecece]"><li>Rigorous quality inspections</li><li>Nationwide shipping</li><li>Competitive pricing</li><li>Secure checkout and easy returns</li><li>Prompt customer support available 7 days a week</li></ul></div><div class="text-left"><h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Drive Your VW Further with PartsCentral</h3><p class="text-[20px] text-[#cecece] leading-[34px] mb-3">Find your model, request a quote, and order with ease. Join thousands of Volkswagen drivers who rely on PartsCentral for reliable, affordable, and high-quality Volkswagen used parts.</p><p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">Request a free quote today.</p></div></div><div class="w-full mt-20 py-16 sm:py-20 px-4 sm:px-8  bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 text-center rounded-2xl"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Find Quality <!-- -->Volkswagen Used Parts for Sale<!-- --> Parts Today?</h2><p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base">Get fast pricing, expert guidance, and nationwide delivery on quality used auto parts for your <!-- -->Volkswagen Used Parts for Sale<!-- -->.</p><a href="/" class="inline-block  bg-[#00A3FF]  text-white px-7 sm:px-9 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,163,255,0.45)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,163,255,0.7)] transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-95">Find My Parts</a></div></section><section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-16 bg-[#07142B] text-[#E8F3FF]"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-orbitron mb-10 text-center">USED <!-- -->VOLKSWAGEN<!-- --> AUTO PARTS</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><ul class="space-y-2 text-lg leading-7 font-jaldi list-disc list-inside text-[#cecece]"><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->Engine Assembly</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->Transmission</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS Control Module</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->ABS System (Anti-Lock)</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Compressor Clutch</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->AC Condenser</li><li>Volkswagen<!-- --> <!-- -->A